metadata.name: Future
metadata.description: It's the year 2167 & after transversing through clusters of galaxies in search of extraterrestrial intelligence, a group of astronauts stumbles upon a structure with strange anomalies, which seems like a product of Kardashev Type II civilization. Only if we could interact with them, we might learn the secret to harnessing the power of our own sun. Will these cybernetics help or not? That's for you to find out.
